it is a two-state option-pricing model
it is based on the assumption of no arbitrage, which means the implication of all risk-free investments earn the risk-free rate of return and no ivestment opportunities exist that require zero dollars of investment buy yield positive returns

it is the activity of many individuals operating within the context of financial markets that, in fact, upholds these conditions.




